PrecisDesignation of DONALD W. BLACK, of Regina, Saskatchewan, Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Farm Credit Corporation, to act as Chief Executive Officer of the Farm Credit Corporation to hold office during pleasure until such time as a President is appointed and is designated as Chief Executive Officer.
